    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't want a \"break\" or \"self-kindness.\" i just want to not feel this way. everything is just so gray. sometimes i think about how peaceful it would be if i could just... stop. if i didn't have to wake up to this silence every single morning. it feels like i'm just existing, but not actually living. it makes me wonder why i'm even still here.",
